1. Videla sam *zgodnu* devojku na ulici. (I saw a *pretty* girl on the street.)
2. Kupila sam *zgodnu* knjigu za poklon. (I bought a *convenient* book as a gift.)
3. Ona je vrlo *zgodna* za ovaj posao. (She is very *suitable* for this job.)
4. Rekla mi je *zgodnu* laž da bi me zaštitila. (She told me a *useful* lie to protect me.)
5. Našla sam *zgodan* način da zaradim dodatni novac. (I found a *clever* way to earn extra money.)
6. Moramo naći *zgodno* vreme da se sastanemo. (We need to find a *convenient* time to meet.)
7. *Zgodno* je što si me pozvao, baš sam htela da te vidim. (It's *nice* that you called me, I wanted to see you.)
8. On je *zgodan* momak, ali nije za ozbiljnu vezu. (He is a *handsome* guy, but not suitable for a serious relationship.)